{"tid":170843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勤力比天資重要？","createTime":"2017-03-25T02:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T16:27:42.000Z","uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02815916f249ea20670565106126ae9bd401d129","tid":170843,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有天資，就唔洗勤力啦..<br />\n無天資，勤力都無用啦..<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efa6181367f8190391ba5290dc52d5000d590de","tid":170843,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T03:01:45.000Z","msg":"無人理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7599a6868e84eb06149c37dc0765b02d9dbc7b7a","tid":170843,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"學得快唔快姐"},{"pid":"34407f2ef8e886333eb4d3e85ae89ca35bfa5c84","tid":170843,"uid":10520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T03:10:28.000Z","msg":"識人好過識字啊傻仔"},{"pid":"5e25582378839a22c4b072734083451d5a0634e7","tid":170843,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T03:14:59.000Z","msg":"其實天資就好似一部靚嘅機體咁，如果你唔勤力去練習各種戰鬥技巧，就算你上到戰場都係等俾人屠"},{"pid":"b5c6089aa082e39085e21eab1387c3b261a2d9d1","tid":170843,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T03:16:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識人好過識字啊傻仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有父幹人脈咪係天資囉..<br />\n無父幹，靠自己努力去識人咪後天勤力囉..<br />\n不服來辯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},